aWFRuleDesc.RuleDescription: The charge is the cost of insurance per unit. One unit is 1000 of coverage amount. COI is based on insured age, and option age.
aWFRuleDesc.RuleText:
; aWF_RT_Formule (aWLIClaimRuleEngineWithCashValue) (Def Version:3) (Implem Version:1)
uses aWFRuleDesc, WFTypes
function CashValue_NetSinglePremium(Age : Int4, Duration : Int4) return Num8 uses aWFStandAloneRule
var tmpRule : aWFRuleDesc
tmpRule = self.GetExactRuleToExecuteFromRankInRuleDesc(0, self.CurrentDate) if tmpRule <> Nil aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).AppendParam(Age, 0, tmpRule) aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).AppendParam(Duration, 1, tmpRule) tmpRule.GetStandAloneResult(_Result, self) aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).CleanParamsAfterExecution(tmpRule) else self.AppendComment('No rule version defined at this date') endIf endFunc
procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : Num8) var COI : tWFAmount var Units : tWFAmount
Units = self.Option__CoverageAmount / 1000 self.AppendComment(Concat('Units:', NaS(Units))) ; COI = self.CashValue_NetSinglePremium(self.Insured__Age__At_Subscription, self.Option__AgeInYears) self.AppendComment(Concat('Cost of Insurance per unit: ', NaS(COI))) ; Result = COI * Units endProc
aWFRuleDesc.Name: Net single Premium per 1,000

aWFRuleDesc.RuleText:
; aWF_RT_Formule (aWLIClaimRuleEngineWithCashValue) (Def Version:2) (Implem Version:1)
uses aWFRuleDesc
function CashValue_ChildTermRider(RiderAmount : Num8) return Num8 uses aWFStandAloneRule
var tmpRule : aWFRuleDesc
tmpRule = self.GetExactRuleToExecuteFromRankInRuleDesc(0, self.CurrentDate) if tmpRule <> Nil aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).AppendParam(RiderAmount, 0, tmpRule) tmpRule.GetStandAloneResult(_Result, self) aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).CleanParamsAfterExecution(tmpRule) else self.AppendComment('No rule version defined at this date') endIf endFunc
procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : Num8) if self.Contract__IsCoverageSubscribed('CTR') Result = self.Contract__CoveredNumberOnCoverage('CTR') * self.CashValue_ChildTermRider(self.Contract__CoverageAmountOfCoverage('CTR')) endIf endProc

procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : Num8) if self.Option__Code = 'NOLAPSE' if self.Subscriber__Age__Exact <= 45 Result = 12.43 / 1000 * 15000 else Result = 22.43 / 1000 * 15000 endIf elseif self.Option__Code = 'WOPCOI' Result = 0 else if self.Insured__Age__Exact <= 45 if self.Option__Dynamic_Data__DeathBenefitOptions = IncreasingDeathBenefit if self.Insured__Classifications__SmokerStatus = NonSmoker Result = 44.43 / 1000 * self.Option__CoverageAmount else Result = 33.43 / 1000 * self.Option__CoverageAmount endIf else if self.Insured__Classifications__SmokerStatus = NonSmoker Result = 66.43 / 1000 * self.Option__CoverageAmount else Result = 55.43 / 1000 * self.Option__CoverageAmount endIf endIf else if self.Option__Dynamic_Data__DeathBenefitOptions = IncreasingDeathBenefit if self.Insured__Classifications__SmokerStatus = NonSmoker Result = 88.43 / 1000 * self.Option__CoverageAmount else Result = 77.43 / 1000 * self.Option__CoverageAmount endIf else if self.Insured__Classifications__SmokerStatus = NonSmoker Result = 110.43 / 1000 * self.Option__CoverageAmount else Result = 100.43 / 1000 * self.Option__CoverageAmount endIf endIf endIf endIf endProc

aWLICoverageOutstandingAmountBroker.OutstandingAmountCalculationType: Sum at Risk Based on Rule

aWFRuleDesc.RuleText:
; aWF_RT_Formule (aWLIClaimRuleEngineWithCashValue) (Def Version:1) (Implem Version:1)
procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : Num8) switch self.Subscriber__Age__Exact when 0 to 40 Result = 250 endWhen when 41 to 45 Result = 215 + 7 * (45 - self.Subscriber__Age__Exact) endWhen when 46 to 50 Result = 185 + 6 * (50 - self.Subscriber__Age__Exact) endWhen when 51 to 55 Result = 150 + 7 * (55 - self.Subscriber__Age__Exact) endWhen when 56 to 60 Result = 130 + 4 * (60 - self.Subscriber__Age__Exact) endWhen when 61 to 65 Result = 120 + 2 * (65 - self.Subscriber__Age__Exact) endWhen when 66 to 70 Result = 115 + (70 - self.Subscriber__Age__Exact) endWhen when 71 to 75 Result = 105 + 2 * (75 - self.Subscriber__Age__Exact) endWhen when 76 to 90 Result = 105 endWhen when 91 to 95 Result = 100 + (95 - self.Subscriber__Age__Exact) endWhen else Result = 100 endSwitch if self.Option__CoverageAmount < self.Option__CashValue * Result / 100 Result = self.Option__CashValue * Result / 100 else Result = self.Option__CoverageAmount endIf endProc

aWFRuleDesc.RuleDescription: Impact on cost basis: -Non MEC: the cost basis is reduced first, then the gain -MEC: the gain is reduced first and then the cost basis (withdrawing from the gain has no impact on the cost basis)
aWFRuleDesc.RuleText:
; aWF_RT_Formule (aWLIClaimRuleEngineWithCashValue) (Def Version:1) (Implem Version:1)
procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : Num8) if not self.Contract__IsMEC if self.DeliveredService__GrossSurrenderAmount <= self.Option__CostBasis Result = -self.DeliveredService__GrossSurrenderAmount else Result = -self.Option__CostBasis endIf else if self.DeliveredService__GrossSurrenderAmount > self.Option__Gain Result = -(self.DeliveredService__GrossSurrenderAmount - self.Option__Gain) else Result = 0 endIf endIf endProc
aWFRuleDesc.Name: Cost Basis Impact

aWFRuleDesc.Name: Cost Basis Impact

aWFRuleDesc.RuleDescription: If MEC and there is some gain on the contract, the gain is taxed and the cost basis needs to be incremented by the gain. (Reminder: once gain has been taxed it becomes cost basis)
aWFRuleDesc.RuleText:
; aWF_RT_Formule (aWLIClaimRuleEngineWithCashValue) (Def Version:1) (Implem Version:1)
procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : Num8) if self.Contract__IsMEC if self.Option__Gain > 0 if self.Option__Gain >= self.Interest__Amount Result = self.Interest__Amount else Result = self.Option__Gain endIf else Result = 0 endIf endIf endProc
aWFRuleDesc.Name: Cost Basis Impact

aWFRuleDesc.RuleDescription: If MEC and there is some gain on the contract, the gain is taxed and the cost basis needs to be incremented by the gain. (Reminder: once gain has been taxed it becomes cost basis)
aWFRuleDesc.RuleText:
; aWF_RT_Formule (aWLIClaimRuleEngineWithCashValue) (Def Version:1) (Implem Version:1)
procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : Num8) if self.Contract__IsMEC if self.Option__Gain > 0 if self.Option__Gain >= self.DeliveredService__AcceptedLoanAmount Result = self.DeliveredService__AcceptedLoanAmount else Result = self.Option__Gain endIf else Result = 0 endIf endIf endProc
aWFRuleDesc.Name: Cost Basis Impact

aWFRuleDesc.RuleDescription: Increasing Death Benefit pays coverage amount minus unpaid loan and loan interest and In addition, the total cash value of contract at date of death. Level Death Benefit pays coverage amount minus unpaid loan and loan interest.
aWFRuleDesc.RuleText:
; aWF_RT_Formule (aWLIClaimRuleEngineWithCashValue) (Def Version:1) (Implem Version:1)
type tWF___DeathBenefitOptions : (IncreasingDeathBenefit, LevelDeathBenefi)
function Option__Dynamic_Data__DeathBenefitOptions return tWF___DeathBenefitOptions type tpValue : .tWF___DeathBenefitOptions
var p : tWF___DeathBenefitOptions
if self.EvaluateFieldDescFromRank(0, 5, 'Option__Dynamic_Data__DeathBenefitOptions') p = tpValue(self.pFieldValue). _Result = p endIf endFunc
procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : Num8) Result = self.Option__CoverageAmount - self.Option__TotalUnPaidLoanAmount if self.Option__Dynamic_Data__DeathBenefitOptions = IncreasingDeathBenefit Result += self.Option__CashValueAtDate(self.Death__DeathDate) endIf endProc

; aWF_RT_Formule (aWLIClaimRuleEngineWithCashValue) (Def Version:2) (Implem Version:1)
function DeliveredService__Dynamic_Data__ExchangedContractisMEC return Boolean type tpValue : .Boolean
var p : Boolean
if self.EvaluateFieldDescFromRank(0, 12, 'DeliveredService__Dynamic_Data__ExchangedContractisMEC') p = tpValue(self.pFieldValue). _Result = p endIf endFunc
procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : Num8) var NSPAmount : Num8
NSPAmount = self.Contract__CalculateNSPAtDate(self.CurrentDate) Result = self.DeliveredService__FreeChoiceForCostBasis self.Set_Value__GuideLinePremiumIncrease(self.DeliveredService__PurchaseAmount) if NSPAmount <> 0 self.Set_Value__UpdateSevenPayPremiumLimit(self.Contract__CalculateSevenPayPremiumLimitAtDate(self.CurrentDate) * (1 - self.DeliveredService__PurchaseAmount / NSPAmount)) endIf if self.DeliveredService__Dynamic_Data__ExchangedContractisMEC = True self.Set_Value__SetContractAsMEC endIf endProc
